Story: Roman Number Converter

Meta:
@scope interview

Narrative:
    As a User
    I should be able to convert integer to Roman Numbers

Scenario: 1
When input number is 1
Then corresponding roman representation is I

Scenario: 2
When input number is 5
Then corresponding roman representation is V

Scenario: 3
When input number is 10
Then corresponding roman representation is X

Scenario: 4
When input number is 400
Then corresponding roman representation is CD

